Link to video : Aftermath of fatal earthquake in Sichuan , China At least 156 people are dead and more than 5 , 500 injured after a powerful earthquake rocked Sichuan , in south - west China , on Saturday morning , officials said . The 6 . 6 - magnitude shock is believed to have been on the same fault as the devastating quake that left 70 , 000 dead and another 18 , 000 missing in the province five years ago .